  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AbbreviationProvider
    Retrieves abbreviations for titles, authorities, institution names, etc.
    ItemDataProvider
    Retrieves citation items
    LocaleProvider
    Provides the serialized XML representation for a locale
    VariableWrapper
    Decorates individual items in citations and bibliographies
